ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of TRACY PRIMEAU of Kincardine, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Matthew A. Lafrenière, whose term has expired.
